{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/addannotations:"]}],"metadata":{"title":"addAnnotations:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)addAnnotations:","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"text":"addAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1808"}},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/addAnnotations:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an array of annotations to the map view."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of annotation objects. Each object in the array"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"must conform to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. The map view retains each"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotation object."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cannot be added to the map view at this time. Nor can "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects that are not instances of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":". Any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, or shape collection objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are specified are silently ignored."}]}],"style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/addAnnotations:":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/addannotations:","abstract":[{"text":"Adds an array of annotations to the map view.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/addAnnotations:","title":"addAnnotations:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"title":"MLNMultiPolyline","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolyline"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"title":"MLNPolyline","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPoint":{"title":"MLNMultiPoint","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPoint"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is an abstract superclass used to define shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"composed of multiple vertices."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"title":"MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview"}}}